title: Alabama man who stole the identities of prison inmates, Pittsburgh residents gets prison time
text:
Published By: Al.com: Montgomery - Today 
A Montgomery County man was ordered to serve 48 months in prison for his involvement in a stolen identity tax refund fraud scheme....
